title: Wild Arms II
description: Ashley, Lilka and Brad are recruited into a special squad, ARMS, to help combat the terrorist organization Odessa. Wild Arms 2 introduces more playable characters than the original game, as well as a rotatable 3D world and more character development options. Of course, there's more in terms of threats to Filgaia than Odessa, and it's up to Ashley and his friends to find out what it is.
